title: cardigan
description:
Is this the first mention of the love triangle, or is the story told out of order? We discuss the theory behind the underlying story of this album, the real trilogy that we are hoping for, and our thoughts on TS 10... all while breaking down cardigan!
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? Please let us know!
